By subjectum is meant the subjectum operationis, or materia eirca quam, more properly called the object; by media, the means by which out of this matter the end is produced. In building, e. g the house is the end; the materials the subject: the act of building, the means. In Efflics, as treated by Aristotle‚ happiness is the end: man the subject; virtue the means.
